title: Unreasonable - Urban Kitesurfing with Kevin Langeree
description:
During one of the strongest wind storms of the year, O'Neill kitesurfer Kevin Langeree decided to be a bit unreasonable.

With 50+ knots of wind, Kevin took to the water for an urban kiteboard session in Amsterdam.

The goal: Reach Amsterdam Central Station and not to get busted by the police along the way.

Additional Hazards: Oil Tankers, Ferries and Unpredictable winds.
